1. *Kazem* da ću sutra ići na more. (I say that I will go to the sea tomorrow.)
2. Ne znam, *kažem* samo ono što vidim. (I don't know, I just say what I see.)
3. *Kažem* ti da je sve u redu. (I'm telling you that everything is okay.)
4. On *kaže* da je u pravu. (He says he is right.)
5. *Kazemo* da ćemo biti tu do kraja godine. (We say we will be here until the end of the year.)